        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop the <strong>tomato[es]</strong> into wedges</p><p>Dissolve your<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><strong>chicken stock mix</strong> in 100ml<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span><span class=\"text-purple\">[125ml]</span><span class=\"text-danger\"> [150ml] </span><strong>boiled water</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
