    {
      "instruction": "<p>Push the <strong>browned lean beef mince</strong> to one side of the pan</p><p>Add your <strong>ground cumin </strong>and<strong> garam masala</strong> to the other side of the pan and cook for 1-2 min until fragrant</p>",
