    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add the<strong> tomato wedges </strong>and <strong>chicken</strong> <strong>stock</strong> to the pan and stir everything together</p><p>Cook for 1-2 min or until reduced and the beef is cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>spiced lean beef mince</strong></p>",
